column1:
Quite a view. Considering everything is over
now, I can appreciate this view that much more.

[1B]S1... Why didn't you invite Lady
Ann...?
Are you even listening to me!?
Come on, a place like this is supposed to be, you know... romantic.
Hey, this ain't so bad either, right? It's a night for the boys, know what I'm sayin'?

Agreed, having friends is quite important. I'm
nearly out of travel funds and almost couldn't
afford the entry fee.

...Hey, you better pay me back once we're home,
ya hear?

Of course. However, I ask that you give me time
to compose another winning piece.

Damn, I'm kinda in the same boat. I was startin'
to wonder what was gonna happen first: me
runnin' out of money, or us beating Konoe.

Indeed, if this trip continued any longer, I would
have had to start asking everyone for money.
*sigh* Come on, let's just take in the view.

...We've taken down Konoe. There won't be any
more Jails now.
Osaka is safe, thanks to you. Great job, guys.

Heh, that's just 'cause you did such a great job
leadin' the rest of us.
I agree. However, we can't rest easy just yet.

EMMA still needs to get shut down, and Owada's
not behind bars.
But let's leave that to Zenkichi. I know he'll come through.
All right, how 'bout we take a picture of the view here and send it over to Gramps to motivate him?

Give him a good look at the city he helped
protect!
That's not a bad idea... Though I would prefer we add some flair in hopes we might arouse even greater passion.
I have an idea, then. Ryuji, get on the ground.

Okay, now [1B]S1, Morgana, you
both get on top!
No! It ain't! And why the hell're we doin' this!?
We took in the nighttime sights of Osaka...
I feel like our bonds have grown stronger...

It was about time to go, so we went
to meet everyone for the celebration...
